response.content:
```sql
SELECT
  sum(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM orders.created_at) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE()) THEN order_items.sale_price ELSE 0 END) AS this_year_sales,
  sum(CASE WHEN EXTRACT(YEAR FROM orders.created_at) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE()) - 1 THEN order_items.sale_price ELSE 0 END) AS last_year_sales
FROM
  `thelook_ecommerce.model.orders` AS orders
  INNER JOIN `thelook_ecommerce.model.order_items` AS order_items ON orders.order_id = order_items.order_id
WHERE
  orders.status NOT IN ('Cancelled', 'Returned')
  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM orders.created_at) IN (
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE()),
    EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE()) - 1
  )
```
